title.en: My food's getting cold, of course.

comment.en: The sheer effort some creatures expend reminds me of my own battle with the coffee machine.
comment.es: Tanto esfuerzo... como yo con la cafetera.
comment.pt-BR: Me lembra a cafeteira. Minha batalha diária.

title.en: The food's getting cold. Knew it.
title.es: Just sat down. Already time to get up?
title.pt-BR: Just sat down. Break's already gone.

comment.en: Sometimes I think they have it right, just existing without quite so many expectations.
comment.es: Uno se cansa. Quizá mejor sin tantas exigencias.
comment.pt-BR: Até que eles estão certos em só viver, né?

title.en: My food just got cold. Perfect.
title.es: Shift ended. My life didn't start.
title.pt-BR: My lunch is getting cold. Whatever.

comment.en: Another day, another instinct I mostly try to ignore.
comment.es: Otro día, otro instinto que, bueno, intento.
comment.pt-BR: Mais um dia, mais um que finjo que não vejo.

title.en: My food's getting cold. Just like everything else.
title.pt-BR: My break food gets cold again. Expected.

comment.en: If only my spirit could regenerate with such effortless biological efficiency.
comment.es: Ojalá mi espíritu se regenerara así de fácil.
comment.pt-BR: Quem me dera recarregar o ânimo assim.

title.es: My food's cold again. Knew it.
title.pt-BR: My food's getting cold again, of course.

comment.en: It's remarkable how some creatures endure; I just endure another Monday.
comment.es: Qué aguante... A uno le toca otro lunes.
comment.pt-BR: Alguns são admiráveis. A gente só sobrevive à segunda.
